					"markdown": "**Download your favorite Clips, VODs and Live Streams with Dvnloader for Twitch!**\n\nEnhance your Twitch experience with this powerful tweak! Unlock the ability to download your favorite Twitch videos effortlessly. Save and enjoy content on your own terms with feature-packed tweak designed for video enthusiasts. Seamlessly download a variety of content, including profile photos, clips, videos, and live broadcasts, with a simple long-press gesture. Enjoy the convenience of background downloads and receive notifications upon completion for a hassle-free experience.\n\n**TLDR:**\n- Clip downloading. This includes both clips from user profiles and those created by tapping the clip button\n- Full video downloading or specified duration\n- Live broadcast downloading with specified duration or until the end of the broadcast\n- Profile photo viewing\n- The ability to cancel downloading. Optionally, you can save the already downloaded part of the canceled download\n- Supports background downloading. You don't need to remain in the Twitch app and monitor every percentage of the download - TwitchDvn will notify you when the download is complete\n\n**Refund policy:**\nNot eligible for a refund, except in cases where the issue lies with the tweak itself and the said issue cannot be resolved.",
